    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚立法者同意弹劾副总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/kenyan-lawmakers-agree-to-impeach-deputy-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚立法者投票弹劾副总统里加蒂·加查瓜，这增加了在该国经济难以从今年早些时候的致命反政府抗议活动中复苏之际再次出现政治不稳定的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/kenyan-lawmakers-agree-to-impeach-deputy-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 18:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯抓住特朗普向普京寄送新冠检测设备的传闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/claim-that-trump-sent-putin-covid-test-devices-draws-harris-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯试图利用记者鲍勃·伍德沃德的新书报道，该书指控前总统唐纳德·特朗普在任期间在疫情最严重时期向俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京发送了新冠检测设备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/claim-that-trump-sent-putin-covid-test-devices-draws-harris-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 18:02:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政府经受住了左翼联盟的不信任投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/french-government-survives-leftist-alliance-s-no-confidence-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府周二经受住了左翼议员提出的不信任动议，他们认为法国政府的组成和政策并未反映最近立法选举的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/french-government-survives-leftist-alliance-s-no-confidence-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 17:43:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ternium 押注拉美抵御中国钢铁威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ternium-ceo-says-mexico-needs-clear-rules-for-private-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉美最大钢铁制造商 Ternium SA 首席执行官马克西莫·维多亚 (Maximo Vedoya) 表示，该公司正在大力推进增长计划，并认为该地区各国政府已经意识到来自中国的不公平竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ternium-ceo-says-mexico-needs-clear-rules-for-private-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 17:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登吹嘘计划在摇摆州更换美国铅管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/all-us-lead-pipes-to-be-replaced-in-decade-under-biden-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在访问选举战场州威斯康星州时宣布了一项在未来 10 年内更换全国所有铅管的计划，并承诺从环境保护署额外拨款 26 亿美元用于改善饮用水。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/all-us-lead-pipes-to-be-replaced-in-decade-under-biden-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡反对，以色列国防部长推迟访美之行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/israel-defense-chief-to-head-to-us-as-iran-retaliation-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼发言人周二表示，以色列国防部长访美计划被推迟，该计划原本是为美以盟友制定共同战略以应对伊朗威胁的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/israel-defense-chief-to-head-to-us-as-iran-retaliation-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 06:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
